<div class="memdoc">

<p>
As descriped in PKCS5, convert a password, salt, and iteration counter into a crypto key.<p>
<dl compact><dt><b>Parameters:</b></dt><dd>
  <table border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0">
